Purpose of use of personal information
Personal information provided by customers, including name, address, telephone number, and e-mail address, will be used for the following purposes. If we wish to use your personal information beyond the scope of the purpose of use, we will obtain your prior consent.
To manage membership from registration to withdrawal
To fulfill orders received
To carry out packing and shipping of products, etc.
To respond to inquiries, complaints, consultations, etc. regarding our services.
To distribute e-mail newsletters
Sending of email notifications of campaigns and new product information, etc.
To respond to various inquiries and after-sales services
Notification of matters necessary for the operation of this website
